<title>ạhtfwạ ṣqfwạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạhtfwạ ṣqfwạ ạnsẖrwạ mḥbẗ yswʿ lkl ạlnạs
 yswʿ rby bygẖfr kl ạldẖnwb yswʿ rby byṣlḥ kl ạlʿywb
 yswʿ rby bynwr kl ạlqlwb ylạ bynạ nsbḥ ạlly ḥbnạ
 2- ạhtfwạ ṣqfwạ ạnsẖrwạ tsbyḥ yswʿ lkl ạlnạs
 tsbyḥ yswʿ yfrḥ rbnạ tsbyḥ yswʿ yfrḥ qlbnạ
 tsbyḥ yswʿ fy ạlḍyq yfknạ ylạ bynạ nsbḥ ạlly ḥbnạ</lyrics>
</song>